            <p>The Alumni Affairs Reference Collection was compiled by University Archives staff from a variety of sources.
This collection was extracted from a vertical file on alumni which included record and non-record materials about alumni, the Alumni Association and the Alumni Affairs office. The materials were received in mailings, either to the Archives office or to Archives staff involved in alumni activities.
